{"tid":1916023,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"不如開返間環保醫院俾環保撚","createTime":"2020-03-08T15:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T12:38:54.000Z","uid":232237,"like":67,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2c2ac77fe84d5b0ed405597335ed34dee81cacc8","tid":1916023,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"暫時諗法係，醫院所有野都要合符環保撚嘅環保同天然做原則。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫院入面所有耗材都會循環再用，包括針筒、紗布、綿花之類，全部用完，洗返淨就俾下手用。而消毒一定唔可以用酒精，要用醋、檸檬汁呢d懶係天然嘅消毒劑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而醫院一定絕對唔可以開冷氣，最多只可以開風扇！手術就晌密不透風而乾燥嘅房間做，好似以前太監切jj嘅蠶室咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有攞藥一定要自備盛器，而食剩嘅藥可以交返俾姑娘，倒返出黎俾第二個。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有d咩可以再環保D?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10af5da02466fe87d952e772fbe65bb48ac0556e","tid":1916023,"uid":254167,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"食唔曬嘅飯分享比其他病友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38160e9df86c3fa0f060b4053cd5e88fd9acd29e","tid":1916023,"uid":100044,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:37:14.000Z","msg":"直接唔好比人出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccae01cd2737f4d43540ed07e1b45d6908676be9","tid":1916023,"uid":153531,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:38:21.000Z","msg":"收工口罩吹返乾俾下更用"},{"pid":"df531b9ea272238c30b8434896eee67b9219938d","tid":1916023,"uid":34517,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:38:24.000Z","msg":"啲尿片濕左 曬乾佢再用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5d0f41375a0650e0d5f761cd466ff82cbc1c1e","tid":1916023,"uid"